properties.areaDesc: Southern Lander County and Southern Eureka County; White Pine County
properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued February 9 at 2:43AM PST until February 9 at 7:00PM PST by NWS Elko NV
properties.description:
* WHAT...Northeast winds 20 to 30 mph with gusts up to 50 mph
expected.

* WHERE...White Pine County and Southern Lander County and
Southern Eureka County.

* WHEN...From 10 AM this morning to 7 PM PST this evening.

* IMPACTS...Gusty winds could blow around unsecured objects. A few
power outages are possible.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 10 AM THIS MORNING TO 7 PM PST THIS EVENING
